{"tid":2307715,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS打破告示牌60年紀錄！　韓文歌空降奪冠「全專輯都上榜」","createTime":"2020-12-01T10:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:19:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cff40b0f4076149b1727dcb609e790a5bb8b7426","tid":2307715,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"南韓天團防彈少年團（BTS）今年接連以英文單曲《Dynamite》、合作混音單曲《Savage Love》拿下美國告示牌音樂榜（Billboard Charts）冠軍，1日再創新紀錄，新歌《Life Goes On》再度空降告示牌冠軍，而這也是該榜單成立60年來，第一次有非英文的單曲空降榜單冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5306/d5306567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5306%2Fd5306567.jpg&h=3982189d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團以新歌《Life Goes On》再度告拿下告示牌單曲榜冠軍。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n防彈少年團新歌《Life Goes On》由於是韓文歌曲，目前在美國市場中，仍然不是廣播電台播放歌曲的選項，因此在幾乎沒有電台播放分的情況下，意外的以空降之姿拿下冠軍，讓業界和粉絲都相當驚喜。且由於電台播放分佔有一定比重，因此過去60年來，從來沒有非英文的單曲空降榜單冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5306/d5306565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5306%2Fd5306565.jpg&h=7ba71fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團以新歌《Life Goes On》再度告拿下告示牌單曲榜冠軍。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n而隨著《Life Goes On》空降冠軍，《Dynamite》也回到榜單前十名，拿下本週告示牌音樂榜第三名。值得一提的是，防彈少年團新專輯《BE》當中的歌曲，除了一首是單純紀錄成員們閒聊、沒有旋律和歌詞的《Skit》外，其他6首歌曲全數都上了告示牌HOT 100的榜單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5306/d5306566.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5306%2Fd5306566.jpg&h=f5281803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團《Life Goes On》拿下冠軍，打破告示牌60年來的紀錄。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n突如其來的好消息也令成員十分感動，因手術正在靜養的SUGA，率先在官方社群留下一排「ㅠㅠ」哭哭符號，表達激動的心情。JIMIN也深夜發文，感謝粉絲再度送給他們的大禮。7人也久違合體，錄下在練習室興奮尖叫的影片。先前拿下冠軍時，正好都碰上成員生日，而12月4日也是大哥JIN的生日，再為BTS的成員添一份生日大禮。"},{"pid":"f9380e7710342ea2e8965b40aa713f5f03243149","tid":2307715,"uid":93096,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"又bts<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcaf00161cc2ce7aacc7a5d05c1d822dd199f0f","tid":2307715,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9380e7710342ea2e8965b40aa713f5f03243149","tid":2307715,"uid":93096,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"又bts<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faf57fda2c08efca17862fe95d5d4b2e051d794","tid":2307715,"uid":159583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"中國又嬲"},{"pid":"dd3abec5c8fabf13ed02ae2d8b2bbd24d847d2ec","tid":2307715,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"bts好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569f43e51ccb611cc639269b6ccf5e7dbdb5c03a","tid":2307715,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:52:50.000Z","msg":"我唔信Despacito係首非英文歌當年無拎過榜首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90be14216febd8b3ce9ef0cc021a03b91e94ada7","tid":2307715,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd3abec5c8fabf13ed02ae2d8b2bbd24d847d2ec","tid":2307715,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"bts好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:52:55.000Z","msg":"Be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gi